     <li>
      Add menu item for opening discs
     </li>
     <li>
      Block cursor autohide when volume popup is open in windowed mode
     </li>
     <li>
      Fix crash with mpv 0.30
     </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
     This listing is incomplete. See git log for complete changelog.
    </p>
   </description>
  </release>
